sequenceDiagram
    participant H as Human
    participant A as Agent
    
    H ->> A: run application
    A ->> A: provide (system prompt)
    
    create participant M as Model (LLM)
    A ->> M: connect (external) or create (local)

    Note over H, A: Session Loading
    H ->> A: `/switch session`
    A ->> A: load (session)

    Note over H, A: Conversation
    loop
        A ->> H: ask for input
        H -->> A: input(prompt)
        A ->> M: invoke<br />⚙️ SYSTEM PROMPT=System Prompt<br/>❓ ROLE=User, TEXT=Historical Prompt<br/>✨ ROLE=Assistant, TEXT=Historical Answer<br/>❓ ROLE=User, TEXT=prompt
        A ->> M: invoke<br />⚙️ SYSTEM PROMPT=System Prompt<br/>❓ ROLE=User, TEXT=Historical Prompt<br/>✨ ROLE=Assistant, TEXT=Historical Answer<br/>❓ ROLE=User, TEXT=Historical Prompt<br/>✨ ROLE=Assistant, TEXT=Historical Answer<br/>[...]<br/>❓ ROLE=user, TEXT=prompt
        M -->> A: answer
    end

    A ->> H: ask for input
    H -->> A: `/exit`
    Note over A, M: Termination
    A ->> M: disconnect or destroy
    destroy M
